GTLive is BACK with more Undertale Fan Games! We've laughed, cried, and pulled our hair out with these before...so obviously we're back for MORE! This fan game takes place after the pacifist run of Undertale, and Sans is hard at work trying to find Gaster. Will we be able to locate the elusive W.D. Gaster? Or will we be left in the dark?

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
